---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="CapCity Presents started in Olympia's hardcore, punk, and metal scene and books independent shows with DIY and all-ages values.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1>About CapCity Presents</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="panel prose">
        <p>CapCity Presents started in Olympia in 2015, when Joey Cristina pulled together Andy Moreno and other local promoters to work under one name instead of treating every show like a turf war.</p>
        <p>The project came out of hardcore, punk, metal, and DIY spaces. That still matters. All-ages access is not a marketing angle here; it is an ethical standard.</p>
        <p>CapCity books and promotes local and touring artists across Olympia and Western Washington, with a focus on clear show information, strong local bills, and rooms that make sense for the artists and audience.</p>
        <div class="actions"><a class="button primary" href="/events/">See upcoming shows</a><a class="button" href="/contact/">Contact CapCity</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>People</h2>
        <p>The people behind CapCity Presents.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="people-grid">
        <article class="panel prose person-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Founder / booking</p>
          <h3>Joey Cristina</h3>
          <p>Joey started CapCity Presents in 2015 after years of booking DIY shows in Olympia and seeing too much needless competition in the local promoter scene.</p>
          <p>He brought Andy and others together to build a shared name for Olympia shows. Joey has been booking and promoting in the area since as early as 2006, with hundreds of DIY shows behind him and a long-running commitment to all-ages access.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="panel prose person-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Booking / promotion</p>
          <h3>Andy "Remex" Moreno</h3>
          <p>Andy began booking shows in November 2011 and became a steady Northwest contact for touring musicians, agents, and local artists looking to play Olympia.</p>
          <p>His work across different corners of independent music helped CapCity connect touring bands with local support, practical rooms, and audiences that actually show up.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
